## Naner Portable Nano Configuration

## Basic Settings
set autoindent          # Auto-indent new lines
set tabsize 4           # Tab size of 4 spaces
set tabstospaces        # Convert tabs to spaces
set smooth              # Smooth scrolling
set linenumbers         # Show line numbers
set mouse               # Enable mouse support
set softwrap            # Soft-wrap long lines

## Display
set titlecolor bold,white,blue
set statuscolor bold,white,green
set keycolor bold,white,blue
set functioncolor white

## Backup
# set backup            # Create backup files
# set backupdir "~/.nano/backups"

## Search
set casesensitive       # Case-sensitive search by default
set regexp              # Use regular expressions for search

