## Key Bindings (Emacs-style)
bind ^S savefile main
bind ^Q exit all
bind ^F whereis all
bind ^R replace main
bind ^G help all
bind ^A mark main
bind ^C copy main
bind ^X cut main
bind ^V paste all
bind ^Z undo main
bind ^Y redo main

## Additional useful bindings
bind ^W writeout main
bind ^O insert main
bind ^T gotoline main
bind ^P location main

## Custom syntax highlighting for common files

## .env files
syntax "env" "\.env.*$"
color cyan "^[A-Z_][A-Z0-9_]*="
color yellow "".*""
color brightblack "(^|[[:space:]])#.*$"

## .gitignore files
syntax "gitignore" "\.gitignore$"
color cyan "^[^#].*$"
color brightblack "^#.*$"
color yellow "^\*.*$"
color green "^!.*$"

## Configuration files
syntax "conf" "\.(conf|config|ini)$"
color cyan "^[[:space:]]*[^=]*="
color yellow ""[^"]*""
color brightblack "^[[:space:]]*[;#].*$"
color magenta "^\[.*\]$"

## Dockerfile
syntax "Dockerfile" "Dockerfile.*$"
color brightblue "^(FROM|MAINTAINER|RUN|CMD|EXPOSE|ENV|ADD|COPY|ENTRYPOINT|VOLUME|USER|WORKDIR|ARG|LABEL|SHELL)[[:space:]]"
color yellow ""[^"]*""
color brightblack "^[[:space:]]*#.*$"

